data.description:
Come check out this gem in the heart of Ludlow. This home will take you back in time with its high ceilings, grand staircase, spacious rooms with beautiful hardwood floors (Level 1).  The upgraded kitchen is fully equipped with SS appliances,  upgraded cabinetry, and granite countertops.  First floor laundry with W/D included. The bathroom is large with a dual head shower,  solid wood vanity, granite top with a Grecian style gold sink.   Tons of character here with stained glass window, and original woodwork,.  Large bedrooms all with light/ceiling fans.  One car detached garage for off street parking or storage?  Minutes to downtown Cincy, Devou Park, 
I-75/I-71
